readability_reflection: I have little experience with interpolation, so concatenation felt familiar, also due to using the more familiar + symbol.
comprehension_debugging: Yes, my lack of familiarity with interpolation made understanding of some snippets more difficult, and vice versa for concatenation.
preference_rationale: I would prefer string concatenation because it requires a linear combination of strings, whereas concatenation requires specified calculations, particularly for digits.
learning_curve: My familiarity with concatenation made problems related to concatenation much more easy and feel less stressful.
